AUDIO: 'So, I\'m pretty sure I\'m preaching to the choir on this one. So, maybe not a hot take when I say a music score and audio and sound effects can have a profound impact on the viewing experience of a movie. So, yeah, great music and audio can elevate a great movie. And well, I'

